<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90272740-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799"><num value="2799">§ 2799.</num><heading> Purpose</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this subchapter is to authorize the President to support, consistent with the CFE Treaty, a NATO equipment transfer program that will—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id90272741-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> enhance NATO’s forces,</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id90272742-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> increase NATO standardization and interoperability, and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id90272743-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2799/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> better distribute defense burdens within the NATO alliance.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id90272744-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/629">Pub. L. 90–629</ref>, ch. 9, § 91, as added <ref href="/us/pl/102/228/s2">Pub. L. 102–228, § 2</ref>, <date date="1991-12-12">Dec. 12, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/1691">105 Stat. 1691</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
